Hello,


I am starting to use the version 4 of DAYSIM. Simulation is running OK and
no errors are displayed but the output intgain.csv file *does not show the
activation of electric lighting. It is as if the system is not activated at
all but that does not make sense due to the minimum illuminance level
defined*. I tried other room archives, checked the electric lighting
keywords in the header file etc. but it is not working.


I would appreciate if someone could point to me where to look for the
probable error. The files I am testing now are availabe at this link:
*https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=0B1Lk6lLtyxfUYjY5QXJXeGxRTGc&usp=sharing
<https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=0B1Lk6lLtyxfUYjY5QXJXeGxRTGc&usp=sharing>*




Thanks in advance,




*............. Kamila Mendonça ..............*
Doutoranda do Instituto de Arquitetura e Urbanismo
Universidade de São Paulo


PhD Student at Institute of Architecture and Urbanism
University of São Paulo
